Package: galigor
Title: Collection of Packages For Internet Marketing
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alexey Seleznev", "Netpeak", , email = "selesnow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Author: Alexey Seleznev [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Alexey Seleznev <selesnow@gmail.com>
Description: Collection of packages for work with API 'Yandex Direct',
    'Yandex Metrica', 'MyTarget', 'Vkontakte' and 'Facebook'. This packages 
	allows you loading data from ads account and manage your ads materials.
